{"product_id":"hoia-moisturizing-lip-balm-with-ectoin-14ml","title":"HOIA Lip Balm with Ectoine 14ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"329\"\u003eHOIA Lip Balm with Ectoine is a lip balm containing ectoine, an active ingredient that protects the skin in extreme conditions. This balm is a true lifesaver for your lips, especially in autumn and winter in our climate. In addition, the lip balm contains deeply hydrating hyaluronic acid, nourishing oils, and butters.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"331\" data-end=\"410\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\"\u003eThe lip balm moisturizes and protects your lips, leaving them wonderfully soft.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply on lips.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e *Cocos Nucifera oil, *Theobroma Cacao butter, Ectoin, *Cera Alba, Fragaria Ananassa oil, Punica Granatum oil, Gardenia Tahitensis Flower Extract, Sodium Hyaluronate, Ricinus Communis seed oil, Hydronated Ricinus Communis Seed oil, Helianthus Annuus Seed oil, Tocopherol, Fragaria Ananassa Fruit extract. *Organic. **Natural component of essential oil.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51104858079559,"sku":null,"price":11.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-lip-balm-with-ectoine-14ml-932410.png?v=1740808670","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/hoia-moisturizing-lip-balm-with-ectoin-14ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}